title: psycopg2.errors.UniqueViolation: could not create unique index "api_example_uuid_key"
body:
cf:
https://ajrbyers.medium.com/django-migrations-and-uuid-fields-4e3b27701e4a



Making staticfiles
Initializing database
Operations to perform:
  Apply all migrations: admin, api, auth, authtoken, contenttypes, django_celery_results, django_drf_filepond, sessions, social_django
